  ΔH =   -6:    600 (5.9%)
  ΔH =   -4:   1200 (11.7%)
  ΔH =   -2:   1800 (17.6%)
  ΔH =    0:   2240 (21.9%)
  ΔH =    2:   1800 (17.6%)
  ΔH =    4:   1200 (11.7%)
  ΔH =    6:    600 (5.9%)
  ΔH =    8:    360 (3.5%)
  ΔH =   12:     40 (0.4%)

  All ΔH even? True
  ΔH range: [-12, 12]
  ΔH = ±2 accounts for: 35.2%

